cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning-based AI systems and their susceptibility to adversarial attacks in image classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper proposes a statistical approach for adversarial detection, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
